      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 75.1 - 老子 75.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 75.1 - 老子 75.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>民之饑，以其上食稅之多，是以饑。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The people suffer from famine because of the multitude of taxes consumed by their superiors. It is through this that they suffer famine.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
