      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 75.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>民之輕死，以其上求生之厚，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The people make light of dying because of the greatness of their labours in seeking for the means of living.</seg>
      </tuv>
