      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 75.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫唯無以生為者，是賢於貴生。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus it is that to leave the subject of living altogether out of view is better than to set a high value on it.</seg>
